1
00:00:13,040 --> 00:00:16,110
[Houde Building]

2
00:00:29,830 --> 00:00:31,290
This case once again shows

3
00:00:32,880 --> 00:00:35,110
that decoding
the criminal's emotional conflict

4
00:00:35,110 --> 00:00:35,790
is key

5
00:00:35,790 --> 00:00:38,280
to understanding
their criminal motivations.

6
00:00:38,280 --> 00:00:40,610
Why are profilers called "mind hunters"?

7
00:00:41,320 --> 00:00:42,380
Because they study

8
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:43,520
human nature,

9
00:00:44,270 --> 00:00:45,130
the human mind,

10
00:00:45,710 --> 00:00:47,310
and subconscious thoughts.

11
00:00:47,840 --> 00:00:49,700
As I mentioned in the first class,

12
00:00:50,890 --> 00:00:52,620
the best profilers are experts

13
00:00:53,150 --> 00:00:54,840
in psychiatry,

14
00:00:55,520 --> 00:00:56,280
psychology,

15
00:00:57,150 --> 00:00:59,080
especially abnormal psychology,

16
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:02,000
and have rich hands-on experience

17
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,670
as frontline detectives.

18
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:10,080
Because they are the people
closest to criminals.

19
00:01:11,070 --> 00:01:13,330
Not necessarily in physical proximity,

20
00:01:14,039 --> 00:01:15,640
but psychologically close.

21
00:01:15,990 --> 00:01:16,600
Of course,

22
00:01:18,150 --> 00:01:20,410
they are also the ones closest to danger,

23
00:01:21,870 --> 00:01:22,480
because

24
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,280
there are two things

25
00:01:29,280 --> 00:01:30,150
in this world

26
00:01:30,590 --> 00:01:32,520
that cannot be stared at directly—

27
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:34,229
the sun

28
00:01:35,070 --> 00:01:36,200
and the human heart.

29
00:01:37,229 --> 00:01:38,759
The Book of Documents says,

30
00:01:39,000 --> 00:01:41,800
"The human heart
is perilous and unpredictable."

31
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:52,350
Today is my last class here.

32
00:01:53,780 --> 00:01:54,979
There is one question

33
00:01:56,430 --> 00:01:58,630
I've always wanted to talk to you about.

34
00:01:59,509 --> 00:02:01,380
When we deal with criminals,

35
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:03,800
if we look too deeply,

36
00:02:04,470 --> 00:02:06,130
we might see our own darkness,

37
00:02:06,640 --> 00:02:08,169
even perverse psychology.

38
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:11,680
How should we remain calm?

39
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:23,200
When the abyss gazes back at you,

40
00:02:23,850 --> 00:02:24,780
don't be afraid.

41
00:02:26,079 --> 00:02:27,340
We must firmly believe

42
00:02:28,430 --> 00:02:30,230
that we are different from them.

43
00:02:31,740 --> 00:02:34,000
The love, warmth, and beauty of humanity

44
00:02:34,620 --> 00:02:35,280
we have felt

45
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:37,160
throughout our lives

46
00:02:37,910 --> 00:02:39,640
will form a light in our hearts.

47
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,890
No matter how dark a room we enter,

48
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,490
we must never forget

49
00:02:46,630 --> 00:02:48,160
to bring this light with us.

50
00:04:07,750 --> 00:04:13,310
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

51
00:04:13,790 --> 00:04:16,120
[Episode 28]

52
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:23,190
Jiang Hansheng!

53
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,240
Jiang Cheng?

54
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:46,120
How could I forget about you?

55
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:49,240
We could have been friends.

56
00:05:30,070 --> 00:05:30,750
Chief Tan,

57
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,950
this is Jiang Hansheng.

58
00:05:31,950 --> 00:05:32,960
If we keep searching like this,

59
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:34,220
we won't find Zhou Jin.

60
00:05:34,540 --> 00:05:35,690
We need to do the opposite now

61
00:05:35,690 --> 00:05:36,750
and put pressure on him,

62
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:37,750
making him think we have already

63
00:05:37,750 --> 00:05:39,120
taken control of the whole situation

64
00:05:39,120 --> 00:05:40,390
and that it makes no difference
whether he's there or not.

65
00:05:40,390 --> 00:05:41,190
By then,

66
00:05:41,310 --> 00:05:42,560
he will definitely

67
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,159
try to grasp at his last straw

68
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,800
He will go look for Zhou Jin.

69
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,130
How certain are you?

70
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:48,870
Qi Yan's filthy intention is just

71
00:05:48,870 --> 00:05:51,010
to torture me to death
in front of Zhou Jin.

72
00:05:51,010 --> 00:05:52,170
Or do that to her in front of me.

73
00:05:52,170 --> 00:05:54,380
When he reaches a dead end,

74
00:05:54,420 --> 00:05:55,950
he will definitely do that.

75
00:05:59,270 --> 00:06:00,290
Jiang Cheng, Jiang Cheng.

76
00:06:00,290 --> 00:06:01,880
Find a way to let Qi Yan go.

77
00:06:02,350 --> 00:06:03,950
Let him lead us to Zhou Jin.

78
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,280
Hansheng.

79
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,050
Qi Yan,

80
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:29,520
let her go!

81
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:32,130
Officer Zhou, I advise you not to move.

82
00:06:32,530 --> 00:06:33,970
Otherwise,

83
00:06:34,960 --> 00:06:36,820
it would be very dangerous for us—

84
00:06:37,790 --> 00:06:38,790
for both of us.

85
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,600
Hansheng—

86
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:43,590
do you like it when people call you that?

87
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,070
Hansheng.

88
00:06:47,510 --> 00:06:49,240
Do you really think you've won?

89
00:06:51,630 --> 00:06:53,870
The game isn't over yet.

90
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,750
Let's move on to the final part.

91
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,360
I promise that

92
00:06:58,630 --> 00:07:00,760
as long as you finish this game with me,

93
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,440
and I'll let your Officer Zhou go.

94
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:04,320
I promise. I swear.

95
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,560
You have two choices:

96
00:07:08,030 --> 00:07:09,720
shoot me dead

97
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:15,950
and let me die along with Officer Zhou,

98
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:17,800
or...

99
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:20,430
shoot

100
00:07:21,310 --> 00:07:22,230
yourself.

101
00:07:25,290 --> 00:07:27,680
Pay with your life for my brother's.

102
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:31,160
What will you choose?

103
00:07:32,100 --> 00:07:33,560
I'm looking forward to it.

104
00:07:35,190 --> 00:07:36,280
Come on!

105
00:07:36,830 --> 00:07:38,000
Jiang Hansheng!

106
00:07:38,159 --> 00:07:40,000
Make your choice!

107
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:41,480
Hansheng!

108
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:42,480
Don't care about me!

109
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,480
Pull the trigger!

110
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:45,630
Pull the trigger! Don't care about me!

111
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:46,560
Right.

112
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,420
Listen to what Officer Zhou says.

113
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:50,560
She's so worried about your safety.

114
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,630
Hansheng,

115
00:07:51,630 --> 00:07:52,690
what should you do?

116
00:07:53,290 --> 00:07:55,780
Do you want Officer Zhou to die?

117
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,510
Come on.

118
00:07:58,159 --> 00:07:59,760
Make your choice, Hansheng!

119
00:08:00,190 --> 00:08:01,510
Be decisive!

120
00:08:01,630 --> 00:08:02,920
You didn't hesitate at all

121
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,450
when you killed my brother.

122
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,120
Now!

123
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:08,760
For the girl you love,

124
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:12,070
sacrifice yourself!

125
00:08:12,950 --> 00:08:13,870
Qi Yan,

126
00:08:15,990 --> 00:08:18,250
I think you've been wrong about one thing

127
00:08:19,260 --> 00:08:21,260
from the start.

128
00:08:22,030 --> 00:08:22,810
I...

129
00:08:23,930 --> 00:08:25,930
didn't come here to be your hostage.

130
00:08:28,290 --> 00:08:29,220
I...

131
00:08:31,370 --> 00:08:32,770
came here to avenge...

132
00:08:34,110 --> 00:08:35,230
my brother.

133
00:08:45,580 --> 00:08:46,540
Jiang Hansheng.

134
00:08:48,530 --> 00:08:49,460
Jiang Hansheng!

135
00:08:50,650 --> 00:08:51,710
My name is Zhou Jin.

136
00:08:52,030 --> 00:08:52,790
From now on,

137
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:54,160
we're good friends.

138
00:08:54,670 --> 00:08:55,930
No one can bully you anymore.

139
00:08:55,930 --> 00:08:57,360
Officer Jiang!

140
00:09:02,100 --> 00:09:03,100
Protect Zhou Jin.

141
00:09:04,270 --> 00:09:05,600
I must protect Zhou Jin.

142
00:09:05,910 --> 00:09:06,550
Zhou Jin.

143
00:09:07,890 --> 00:09:09,620
I hope you won't get hurt again.

144
00:09:10,750 --> 00:09:11,720
In the future,

145
00:09:11,820 --> 00:09:13,550
I'll definitely face dangers.

146
00:09:14,390 --> 00:09:16,160
But the more dangerous a place is,

147
00:09:16,160 --> 00:09:18,360
the greater the opportunity it offers.

148
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:20,770
I will protect myself.

149
00:09:21,550 --> 00:09:22,200
Zhou Jin,

150
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:24,270
I love you.

151
00:09:26,730 --> 00:09:28,260
When I first met you,

152
00:09:29,870 --> 00:09:31,000
I wanted to have you.

153
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,030
Jiang Hansheng.

154
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:01,830
Junior!

155
00:10:01,940 --> 00:10:02,740
Hurry! Hurry!

156
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:03,730
Junior! Hurry!

157
00:10:04,430 --> 00:10:05,590
Stretcher! Hurry!

158
00:10:05,750 --> 00:10:06,550
Give him a hand!

159
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:07,590
Careful.

160
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:08,630
Careful.

161
00:10:09,150 --> 00:10:09,650
Careful.

162
00:10:09,650 --> 00:10:10,310
Be careful.

163
00:10:12,400 --> 00:10:13,400
Be careful.

164
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:26,190
This person is extremely dangerous

165
00:10:26,190 --> 00:10:27,520
and mentally unstable.

166
00:10:27,790 --> 00:10:28,670
Sniper team,

167
00:10:28,850 --> 00:10:29,850
stay alert.

168
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,240
Jiang Hansheng.

169
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,750
You think you won, right?

170
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,240
You think I'll give up like this?

171
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,200
Jiang Hansheng!

172
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:51,030
Where is Qi Zhen?

173
00:10:51,370 --> 00:10:53,530
Tell her to come and see me!

174
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:56,270
Before your trial,

175
00:10:57,910 --> 00:10:59,510
I'll let her come and see you.

176
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:22,660
Don't move!

177
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:38,910
Haven't you always wanted to know

178
00:11:39,390 --> 00:11:41,240
how Zhou Chuan died?

179
00:11:48,150 --> 00:11:48,870
Zhan Wei,

180
00:11:49,870 --> 00:11:50,800
just wait to die.

181
00:12:36,140 --> 00:12:36,730
Zhou Jin,

182
00:12:37,140 --> 00:12:37,940
you're awake?

183
00:12:38,480 --> 00:12:39,740
I'll go get the doctor.

184
00:12:43,390 --> 00:12:44,190
What's wrong?

185
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,030
Silly.

186
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:49,750
From such a high place,

187
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:53,410
you just jumped without thinking?

188
00:12:54,630 --> 00:12:56,560
I should be the one asking you that.

189
00:12:57,930 --> 00:12:58,740
From now on,

190
00:13:00,740 --> 00:13:02,270
it's my turn to protect you.

191
00:13:04,980 --> 00:13:06,780
You did a good job protecting me.

192
00:13:08,620 --> 00:13:10,550
I really want to kiss you right now.

193
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:13,200
But right now,

194
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:16,570
it seems inconvenient for me to do it.

195
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,920
The sun is really nice today.

196
00:13:45,910 --> 00:13:47,970
And we're wearing matching outfits.

197
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,240
Let's try not to wear matching outfits

198
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,900
like this again in the future.

199
00:13:56,770 --> 00:13:58,030
I'll go get the doctor.

200
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:04,820
She's basically stable now.

201
00:14:05,020 --> 00:14:05,730
But

202
00:14:05,850 --> 00:14:07,030
she still needs to be hospitalized

203
00:14:07,030 --> 00:14:08,500
for observation for a while.

204
00:14:08,500 --> 00:14:09,870
After all, when she fell into the water,

205
00:14:09,870 --> 00:14:11,680
her internal organs were damaged.

206
00:14:11,680 --> 00:14:13,340
And she was in a coma for 3 days.

207
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,240
I was in a coma for 3 days?

208
00:14:17,330 --> 00:14:17,970
Yes.

209
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,640
Get some proper rest.

210
00:14:19,880 --> 00:14:20,940
Thank you, doctor.

211
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:26,870
It has been 3 days?

212
00:14:27,870 --> 00:14:29,270
How is everything going?

213
00:14:30,030 --> 00:14:31,030
What about Qi Yan?

214
00:14:32,340 --> 00:14:34,070
Qi Yan was arrested on the spot.

215
00:14:35,150 --> 00:14:36,200
He got his karma.

216
00:14:38,040 --> 00:14:39,040
What about Qiu Ye?

217
00:14:40,780 --> 00:14:42,510
She was dead when she was found.

218
00:14:43,300 --> 00:14:44,540
But you saved her son.

219
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:54,090
Your mentor asked me
to pass a message to you.

220
00:14:55,270 --> 00:14:56,040
What...

221
00:14:59,230 --> 00:15:00,460
What did he say?

222
00:15:02,310 --> 00:15:03,360
He said well done.

223
00:15:03,870 --> 00:15:04,930
You did a great job.

224
00:15:06,400 --> 00:15:07,620
It's all over.

225
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:10,030
The nightmare of the 8/17 Case

226
00:15:10,030 --> 00:15:10,960
is over.

227
00:15:18,670 --> 00:15:19,360
Zhou Jin,

228
00:15:20,670 --> 00:15:22,080
cry if you want to.

229
00:15:40,870 --> 00:15:41,670
It's all over.

230
00:15:47,510 --> 00:15:48,480
It's all over.

231
00:16:01,310 --> 00:16:01,860
Dad,

232
00:16:02,550 --> 00:16:03,120
Mom.

233
00:16:04,870 --> 00:16:05,720
Chuan's case

234
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,030
is solved.

235
00:16:07,710 --> 00:16:09,240
It was the drug traffickers

236
00:16:09,510 --> 00:16:11,840
who colluded with Zhan Wei and killed him.

237
00:16:16,950 --> 00:16:17,950
It's been 6 years.

238
00:16:18,610 --> 00:16:19,940
I never expected

239
00:16:19,970 --> 00:16:21,450
the result to be like this.

240
00:16:23,550 --> 00:16:24,200
Dad,

241
00:16:24,870 --> 00:16:25,790
are you okay?

242
00:16:28,030 --> 00:16:29,030
We are fine.

243
00:16:29,640 --> 00:16:31,830
Your brother was an upright man.

244
00:16:31,970 --> 00:16:34,170
He always thought the best of everyone.

245
00:16:35,030 --> 00:16:35,630
Dad,

246
00:16:36,200 --> 00:16:37,800
he had always been like this.

247
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:39,960
Since he was a kid,

248
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,120
he has always

249
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:44,640
set high standards for himself.

250
00:16:45,740 --> 00:16:47,340
Right now, he probably hopes

251
00:16:47,790 --> 00:16:48,720
our whole family

252
00:16:49,270 --> 00:16:50,600
can be proud of him.

253
00:16:51,620 --> 00:16:53,220
I'm definitely proud of him.

254
00:16:54,200 --> 00:16:55,390
Your brother

255
00:16:55,410 --> 00:16:56,520
is my pride.

256
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,200
Zhou Jin,

257
00:17:00,160 --> 00:17:01,560
you are also my pride.

258
00:17:20,349 --> 00:17:21,609
My dad just praised me.

259
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,260
That made you so happy?

260
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:25,829
Of course.

261
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:28,030
I was praised twice today.

262
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:29,920
My mentor praised me,

263
00:17:30,010 --> 00:17:31,410
and my dad praised me too.

264
00:17:32,430 --> 00:17:33,720
They are not like you.

265
00:17:34,030 --> 00:17:35,830
Hearing them praise me is harder

266
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:37,850
than getting a first-class merit.

267
00:17:40,160 --> 00:17:41,760
Have you called your family?

268
00:17:42,490 --> 00:17:43,490
They are abroad.

269
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:45,790
I plan to visit

270
00:17:46,270 --> 00:17:47,200
the Prof later.

271
00:17:48,150 --> 00:17:49,110
I'll go with you.

272
00:17:49,310 --> 00:17:50,030
No need.

273
00:17:50,050 --> 00:17:51,250
Get some proper rest.

274
00:17:52,550 --> 00:17:53,310
Sir,

275
00:17:53,680 --> 00:17:55,400
remember to go downstairs
to get the test report.

276
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:55,880
Okay.

277
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:56,600
Thank you.

278
00:17:59,070 --> 00:17:59,800
I'll go then.

279
00:18:00,000 --> 00:18:01,060
Don't move around.

280
00:18:12,790 --> 00:18:14,310
Zhou Jin, how do you feel?

281
00:18:14,310 --> 00:18:15,240
Feeling better?

282
00:18:16,550 --> 00:18:17,750
I'm fine. I'm doing great.

283
00:18:17,750 --> 00:18:18,810
I'm already awake.

284
00:18:30,030 --> 00:18:30,790
You're here?

285
00:18:34,950 --> 00:18:35,880
Are you alright?

286
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:37,590
I'm fine.

287
00:18:41,590 --> 00:18:42,590
Zhan Wei...

288
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,570
tried to escape,

289
00:18:44,110 --> 00:18:45,370
and I brought him back.

290
00:18:57,200 --> 00:18:58,600
Where is Jiang Hansheng?

291
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:01,260
He went downstairs

292
00:19:01,550 --> 00:19:03,000
to get my test report.

293
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:05,440
Good husband.

294
00:19:08,830 --> 00:19:10,430
Your hair is getting longer.

295
00:19:14,790 --> 00:19:16,030
After I get back to Haizhou,

296
00:19:16,030 --> 00:19:17,290
I should get a haircut.

