I'll share everything I know.

581
00:33:38,430 --> 00:33:39,160
That's good.

582
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:43,550
After a while,

583
00:33:44,700 --> 00:33:46,160
I will completely retire.

584
00:33:48,170 --> 00:33:49,690
I'll go back

585
00:33:49,790 --> 00:33:52,290
and spend time
with my little granddaughter,

586
00:33:52,290 --> 00:33:53,480
counting ducks.

587
00:33:54,850 --> 00:33:55,680
From now on,

588
00:33:56,060 --> 00:33:58,060
it'll be the era of you young people.

589
00:33:58,600 --> 00:33:59,800
Keep up the good work.

590
00:34:01,790 --> 00:34:02,960
Tan said

591
00:34:04,070 --> 00:34:06,160
your quick decisions at the scene

592
00:34:07,470 --> 00:34:08,670
saved a lot of people.

593
00:34:11,920 --> 00:34:14,850
Prof, it's been a long time
since you last praised me.

594
00:34:14,949 --> 00:34:16,350
Look at you getting smug.

595
00:34:25,880 --> 00:34:26,510
Prof,

596
00:34:28,139 --> 00:34:29,540
I'm going back tomorrow.

597
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:35,590
Go back.

598
00:34:38,790 --> 00:34:40,050
You should go home now.

599
00:34:51,590 --> 00:34:52,190
Stop.

600
00:34:54,760 --> 00:34:55,480
Take it off.

601
00:34:57,139 --> 00:34:57,970
Take it off.

602
00:35:07,800 --> 00:35:08,460
Put it on me.

603
00:35:15,550 --> 00:35:16,810
Where are the pockets?

604
00:35:18,140 --> 00:35:18,960
Why are you laughing?

605
00:35:18,960 --> 00:35:19,760
You look good.

606
00:35:20,070 --> 00:35:22,870
Wait. When people
wear this kind of coat nowadays,

607
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:24,840
does it look better buttoned up,

608
00:35:24,840 --> 00:35:25,480
or

609
00:35:26,670 --> 00:35:27,670
worn open?

610
00:35:29,030 --> 00:35:30,960
Buttoned up looks more energetic.

611
00:35:31,840 --> 00:35:33,240
There's only one button?

612
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:35,810
How is it? Looks good?

613
00:35:35,840 --> 00:35:36,400
Totally.

614
00:35:36,550 --> 00:35:37,710
Let me walk a few steps for you to see.

615
00:35:37,710 --> 00:35:38,230
Okay.

616
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:45,670
Come on, follow me.

617
00:35:47,810 --> 00:35:48,900
I'll unbutton it.

618
00:35:48,930 --> 00:35:49,670
Look.

619
00:35:50,360 --> 00:35:51,560
-How do I look?
-Prof.

620
00:35:51,640 --> 00:35:52,390
Just wear this

621
00:35:52,390 --> 00:35:54,000
to attend Zhou Jin and my wedding.

622
00:35:54,000 --> 00:35:54,900
Definitely.

623
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:56,380
I will definitely wear it.

624
00:35:58,320 --> 00:35:59,520
The color is too dark.

625
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:08,240
Full of youthful energy.

626
00:36:11,060 --> 00:36:12,430
This is the new intern

627
00:36:12,450 --> 00:36:13,860
in our squad,

628
00:36:14,070 --> 00:36:15,000
Gao Yaojie.

629
00:36:15,230 --> 00:36:16,150
From today on,

630
00:36:17,270 --> 00:36:18,470
you'll be his mentor.

631
00:36:20,310 --> 00:36:21,710
Nice to meet you, Senior.

632
00:36:22,070 --> 00:36:22,760
Senior,

633
00:36:22,990 --> 00:36:24,710
I also graduated
from Jingzhou Police Academy.

634
00:36:24,710 --> 00:36:26,370
Please guide me in the future.

635
00:36:29,560 --> 00:36:30,160
Comrades,

636
00:36:30,190 --> 00:36:32,050
let me introduce a new colleague,

637
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:32,920
Gao Yaojie.

638
00:36:32,920 --> 00:36:34,120
Just call him Yaojie.

639
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:36,230
This is Liu.

640
00:36:36,670 --> 00:36:37,450
Hello, Liu.

641
00:36:37,470 --> 00:36:37,940
Hello.

642
00:36:38,320 --> 00:36:39,000
Bai Yang.

643
00:36:39,320 --> 00:36:41,050
We all call him Little Bai Yang.

644
00:36:41,420 --> 00:36:42,360
Since a newcomer is here,

645
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:43,920
I can't be Little Bai Yang anymore, right?

646
00:36:43,920 --> 00:36:44,780
So Old Bai Yang?

647
00:36:45,560 --> 00:36:46,290
Bai.

648
00:36:46,550 --> 00:36:48,030
Just call me Yaojie in the future.

649
00:36:48,030 --> 00:36:48,760
Look at him.

650
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:50,020
He has a bright future.

651
00:36:50,730 --> 00:36:51,480
Lu Pengfei.

652
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:52,440
Senior Lu.

653
00:36:52,550 --> 00:36:53,550
Hello, Senior Lu.

654
00:36:53,640 --> 00:36:54,290
Yaojie.

655
00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:55,840
Try to talk to him
as little as possible unless necessary.

656
00:36:55,840 --> 00:36:56,840
Come on, let's continue the introduction.

657
00:36:56,840 --> 00:36:57,510
Jun.

658
00:36:58,330 --> 00:36:59,660
Wan Chongshan, Mr. Wan.

659
00:36:59,880 --> 00:37:00,550
Gao Yaojie.

660
00:37:00,870 --> 00:37:01,870
I've heard of you.

661
00:37:02,270 --> 00:37:03,650
You're a good young man.
Keep up the good work.

662
00:37:03,650 --> 00:37:04,910
Zhou Jin, you're back?

663
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:05,920
Dan.

664
00:37:06,110 --> 00:37:06,670
You came just in time.

665
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:07,590
Let me introduce you.

666
00:37:07,590 --> 00:37:08,230
Yaojie.

667
00:37:08,320 --> 00:37:09,250
Say hello to Dan.

668
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:10,110
Hello, Dan.

669
00:37:10,280 --> 00:37:11,030
Hello.

670
00:37:11,720 --> 00:37:13,780
Are... are you close to your due date?

671
00:37:14,330 --> 00:37:14,850
Yes.

672
00:37:16,150 --> 00:37:17,150
How are you doing?

673
00:37:17,320 --> 00:37:18,700
Don't do anything reckless

674
00:37:18,700 --> 00:37:20,300
until you recover, alright?

675
00:37:20,360 --> 00:37:21,440
I'm perfectly fine.

676
00:37:21,440 --> 00:37:22,110
I reported for duty today

677
00:37:22,110 --> 00:37:23,030
and started working immediately.

678
00:37:23,030 --> 00:37:24,720
I can even show you

679
00:37:24,750 --> 00:37:26,150
a one-handed handstand right now.

680
00:37:26,150 --> 00:37:26,800
Alright.

681
00:37:26,830 --> 00:37:27,830
I will

682
00:37:27,950 --> 00:37:29,440
assign you more tasks then.

683
00:37:29,440 --> 00:37:31,170
How have things been recently?

684
00:37:31,560 --> 00:37:34,130
The Jingzhou police started with
Qi Yan and Zhan Wei

685
00:37:34,130 --> 00:37:35,710
and pulled on a loose thread
that unraveled the whole fabric.

686
00:37:35,710 --> 00:37:36,710
The entire Dongsheng Group

687
00:37:36,710 --> 00:37:38,020
is now under investigation.

688
00:37:38,020 --> 00:37:40,070
Just the case files alone are this much.

689
00:37:40,070 --> 00:37:40,670
Yeah.

690
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,440
I'm from Jingzhou.

691
00:37:42,920 --> 00:37:44,280
Now everyone there

692
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:45,410
is talking about it.

693
00:37:45,440 --> 00:37:46,570
You're from Jingzhou?

694
00:37:46,570 --> 00:37:49,030
Then why did you come here
for an internship?

695
00:37:49,510 --> 00:37:50,670
Because of Uncle Yao.

696
00:37:50,670 --> 00:37:51,750
Who? Uncle Yao?

697
00:37:53,380 --> 00:37:54,090
Leader Yao?

698
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,230
When I was in the police academy,

699
00:37:57,230 --> 00:37:59,360
I was sponsored by Uncle Yao all along.

700
00:37:59,550 --> 00:38:00,950
He was like a father to me.

701
00:38:01,710 --> 00:38:02,670
You might think

702
00:38:02,690 --> 00:38:04,750
I'm being a bit childish saying this,

703
00:38:05,190 --> 00:38:07,590
but since Uncle Yao
died in the line of duty,

704
00:38:07,670 --> 00:38:09,940
the only way I can repay him

705
00:38:10,190 --> 00:38:11,510
is to carry on his will

706
00:38:12,080 --> 00:38:13,480
and strive to be a good police officer.

707
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:14,630
That's the spirit!

708
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:17,040
As your senior, I have to say a few words.

709
00:38:17,400 --> 00:38:18,230
Alright, that's enough.

710
00:38:18,230 --> 00:38:20,290
He just got here today. Go easy on him.

711
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:23,090
It's so good to be young.

712
00:38:23,550 --> 00:38:26,380
I was the champion
in the police academy combat competition.

713
00:38:26,380 --> 00:38:28,670
Uncle Yao even came to school
to watch me receive the award.

714
00:38:28,670 --> 00:38:29,670
So that means...

715
00:38:30,330 --> 00:38:32,330
you must be pretty good at fighting.

716
00:38:32,670 --> 00:38:33,920
Then you're in luck.

717
00:38:34,190 --> 00:38:34,840
Zhou Jin,

718
00:38:35,190 --> 00:38:35,990
Officer Zhou,

719
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:37,580
once won second place.

720
00:38:38,230 --> 00:38:39,360
Keep it low-profile.

721
00:38:39,360 --> 00:38:40,320
It's in the past.

722
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:42,240
If there's a chance, we can spar.

723
00:38:43,030 --> 00:38:44,560
No, do it right now. Come on.

724
00:38:45,090 --> 00:38:45,780
Senior,

725
00:38:46,070 --> 00:38:47,480
I'm not looking down on you.

726
00:38:47,480 --> 00:38:48,320
Men and women

727
00:38:48,320 --> 00:38:50,490
have differences in physical fitness.

728
00:38:50,490 --> 00:38:50,850
Well...

729
00:38:50,850 --> 00:38:52,910
I... I'm just afraid I might hurt you.

730
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:55,840
Now I can't accept that. Come on.

731
00:38:57,670 --> 00:38:59,130
I really can't stand this.

732
00:38:59,920 --> 00:39:00,510
Three,

733
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:01,440
two,

734
00:39:01,460 --> 00:39:02,060
one!

735
00:39:02,290 --> 00:39:03,330
Professor Jiang?

736
00:39:10,630 --> 00:39:12,480
You're back to being a police officer
again?

737
00:39:12,480 --> 00:39:13,800
Under the leadership
of the Provincial Bureau,

738
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:14,800
a new crime research lab
is being established

739
00:39:14,800 --> 00:39:16,440
at the Haizhou Public Security Bureau.

740
00:39:16,440 --> 00:39:18,970
It will be
officially inaugurated tomorrow.

741
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:22,800
Then we should call you Director Jiang
from now on.

742
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:24,140
Just call me Hansheng.

743
00:39:26,000 --> 00:39:28,260
I'm used to calling you Professor Jiang.

744
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:31,180
You can call me whatever you want.

745
00:39:34,030 --> 00:39:35,190
I'm used to...

746
00:39:35,190 --> 00:39:36,850
calling you Professor Jiang.

747
00:39:37,550 --> 00:39:39,120
You can call me whatever you want, babe.

748
00:39:39,120 --> 00:39:40,480
He didn't say babe!

749
00:39:40,510 --> 00:39:41,710
Don't talk nonsense!

750
00:39:42,230 --> 00:39:42,840
Wait.

751
00:39:44,440 --> 00:39:45,710
I think the baby is coming!

752
00:39:45,710 --> 00:39:47,030
Hurry! Get her to the hospital!

753
00:39:47,030 --> 00:39:48,550
Don't panic!

754
00:39:48,570 --> 00:39:49,860
Call an ambulance!

755
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:51,150
I'll drive her there.

756
00:39:51,150 --> 00:39:51,710
Be careful!

757
00:39:51,710 --> 00:39:52,280
Drive her there.

758
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:53,010
Don't panic!

759
00:39:53,190 --> 00:39:53,920
Don't panic!

760
00:39:54,110 --> 00:39:54,920
Purse, phone—

761
00:39:54,940 --> 00:39:55,880
bring them all.

762
00:39:55,880 --> 00:39:56,900
Hansheng, drive the car.

763
00:39:56,900 --> 00:39:57,840
Hansheng, drive the car.

764
00:39:57,840 --> 00:39:58,800
Be careful!

765
00:39:58,800 --> 00:39:59,590
To the hospital! To the hospital!

766
00:39:59,590 --> 00:40:00,440
Be careful!

767
00:40:00,600 --> 00:40:01,250
Don't panic!

768
00:40:01,250 --> 00:40:01,770
Dan!

769
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:11,400
I remember our first date

770
00:40:11,400 --> 00:40:12,710
was right here.

771
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:18,160
Back then,
they only had a small cart stall.

772
00:40:20,190 --> 00:40:21,540
It was April then,

773
00:40:22,070 --> 00:40:23,320
and you bought me ice cream.

774
00:40:23,320 --> 00:40:24,230
I was freezing.

775
00:40:25,200 --> 00:40:26,340
I was dressed too formally,

776
00:40:26,340 --> 00:40:27,400
and I was so nervous

777
00:40:27,590 --> 00:40:29,190
that I was sweating all over.

778
00:40:29,440 --> 00:40:31,670
I thought you were taking revenge on me
on purpose.

779
00:40:31,670 --> 00:40:33,070
I was late, wasn't I?

780
00:40:33,230 --> 00:40:35,230
I was 5 hours late for our first date.

781
00:40:35,590 --> 00:40:36,070
No.

782
00:40:36,880 --> 00:40:38,480
I was really happy back then.

783
00:40:38,670 --> 00:40:40,840
You were out on a mission all day
and it was so late,

784
00:40:40,840 --> 00:40:42,570
but you still came out to see me.

785
00:40:48,070 --> 00:40:49,870
What would you two like to drink?

786
00:40:51,330 --> 00:40:52,660
A milk tea with 30% sugar

787
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:53,720
and extra boba, please.

788
00:40:53,720 --> 00:40:54,280
Okay.

789
00:40:56,440 --> 00:40:57,030
Sir,

790
00:40:57,130 --> 00:40:58,340
you look familiar.

791
00:40:59,280 --> 00:41:01,280
You've been here
with your girlfriend before?

792
00:41:01,280 --> 00:41:02,210
I'm his wife now.

793
00:41:04,120 --> 00:41:05,050
Coming right up.

794
00:41:13,990 --> 00:41:14,990
The sunset today

795
00:41:15,260 --> 00:41:16,260
is so beautiful.

796
00:41:18,230 --> 00:41:18,770
Yeah.

797
00:41:19,670 --> 00:41:20,360
So pretty.

798
00:41:44,160 --> 00:41:47,020
I remember you used to say
the sunset was beautiful.

799
00:41:47,710 --> 00:41:49,370
Where exactly is that sunset?

800
00:41:49,590 --> 00:41:51,050
You never took me to see it.

801
00:41:54,670 --> 00:41:55,600
It's right here.

802
00:42:14,280 --> 00:42:15,280
This sunset

803
00:42:15,620 --> 00:42:16,820
is really beautiful.

804
00:42:21,800 --> 00:42:23,060
The wind is picking up.

805
00:42:47,090 --> 00:42:53,770
[Among all the sunsets, secrets,
and regrets, I'm glad I have you]

806
00:42:55,830 --> 00:42:58,310
[The End]
